Subject: Where to obtain Pingcastle Pro Installation Files
Description:
Hello Support Team
Where do we obtain the new Pingcastle Pro Installation files? Before I was able to download them directly from the Pingcastle Website. Also in the Netwrix Account i am not able to see the Pingcastle under Products.

Lukas
Solution_Comment__c: Registering with Netwrix page allowed the PingCastle downloads to show up, customer can now download the installation files
